data.description: You'll fall in love with this 5 bed, 3 bath, 3 level split in the coveted Country Club Estates the moment you walk in. The main level's family room features a cozy fireplace and access to the tranquil backyard patio. The upper floor boasts 3 bedrooms, a full bath, and the master suite has a fully updated 3/4 bathroom. A spacious living room is located right next to the kitchen and dining room that beautifully overlooks the fireplace. The lower level boasts a second family room with loads of space. There are two more bedrooms on the lower level, and another 3/4 bathroom. There's a bonus room that would be perfect for a hobby room. The fully finished 2 stall garage is heated, and connected to an amazing shop that is heated and cooled too! Make sure to see this gem before it's gone!
